♪ Got It…Say Wassup！

249
00:13:20,966 --> 00:13:22,927
♪ Got It…Oh My Goodness！

250
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:27,223
♪ Got It…世界中ひれ伏せ！

251
00:13:27,306 --> 00:13:29,308
♪ Got It…Say Wassup！

252
00:13:29,391 --> 00:13:31,227
♪ Got It…We Want New World…

253
00:13:31,310 --> 00:13:33,312
